    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Responsibilities in Government to Be Shared</strong>&mdash;Unitedly and prayerfully the father and mother should bear the grave responsibility of guiding their children aright.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">1<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"CT 127.1\" data-link=\"23.591\">Counsels to Teachers, Parents, and Students, 127</span>.</span></a></sup>",
