    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "The father and mother should unite in disciplining their children; each should bear a share of the responsibility, acknowledging themselves under solemn obligations to God to train up their offspring in such a way as to secure to them, as far as possible, good physical health and well-developed characters.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">4<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"nol-ink\" title=\"PHJ 4-1-1890\">Pacific Health Journal, April, 1890</span> (<span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"HR 4-1-1877.7\" data-link=\"504.1116\">The Health Reformer, April, 1877</span>).</span></a></sup>",
