    "content": "If parents do not agree, let them absent themselves from the presence of their children until an understanding can be arrived at.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">8<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"RH 3-30-1897\" data-link=\"821.15771\">The Review and Herald, March 30, 1897</span>.</span></a></sup>",
